snippet.title: Furistas Cat Cafe Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Furistas Cat Cafe FREE for iOS and Android: http://onelink.to/furistascatcafe

Welcome to Furistas Cat Cafe! Help your customers find their purrrfect match and customise your cafe to bring the ultimate joy! 

From Runaway Play, the studio that brought you free to play mobile titles such as Flutter, Starlight and Splash, Furistas Cat Cafe captures the personalities of real life cats and will melt your heart.

Website: http://furistascatcafe.com/
Twitter: twitter.com/furistascatcafe
Instagram: instagram.com/playfuristas
Facebook: facebook.com/furistascatcafe
Runaway website: runawayplay.com
